ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectArrangement between the Government of Canada and the European Space Agency concerning the Participation in the advance Research in Telecommunications Systems 4.0 (ARTES 4.0)
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign and to bring into force, or to delegate the authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, the ARRANGEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE EUROPEAN SPACE AGENCY CONCERNING THE PARTICIPATION BY THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA IN THE ADVANCE RESEARCH IN TELECOMMUNICATIONS SYSTEMS 4.0 (ARTES 4.0) PROGRAMME.
